*planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r9 (14 Jun 2004)

  14 Jun 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> -planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r8.ebuild,
  +planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r9.ebuild,
  +files/planet-ccrma-sources.FPULockup-53804.patch:
  Added a patch for the FPU-lockup issue; please see bug #58304 for details. Old
  version removed.

*planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r8 (02 Jun 2004)

  02 Jun 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> -planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r7.ebuild,
  +planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r8.ebuild,
  +files/planet-ccrma-sources.CAN-2004-0181.patch,
  +files/planet-ccrma-sources.CAN-2004-0394.patch,
  +files/planet-ccrma-sources.CAN-2004-0427.patch:
  Added patches for the CAN-2004-0181, CAN-2004-0394, and CAN-2004-0427
  vulnerabilities. Bug #47881.

  31 May 2004; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>
  planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r7.ebuild:
  Masked planet-ccrma-sources-2.4.21-r7.ebuild broken for ppc

